*Dobijemo* (We get) dobre rezultate. (We get good results.)
Nadamo se da ćemo *dobiti* (We hope to get) povoljnu ponudu. (We hope to get a favourable offer.)
Oni su *dobili* (They got) nagradu za svoj rad. (They got a reward for their work.)
Pokušavamo da *dobijemo* (We are trying to get) najbolji mogući rezultat. (We are trying to get the best possible result.)